some-cpp/blob/master\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">BeeCrypt<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//botan.randombit.net/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Botan<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>： C++加密库</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.cryptopp.com/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Crypto++<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：一个有关加密方案的免费的C++库</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.gnupg.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">GnuPG<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>： OpenPGP标准的完整实现</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.gnutls.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">GnuTLS<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a> ：实现了SSL，TLS和DTLS协议的安全通信库</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.gnu.org/software/libgcrypt/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Libgcrypt<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/fffaraz/awesome-cpp/blob/master\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">libmcrypt<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.libressl.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">LibreSSL<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：免费的SSL/TLS协议，属于2014 OpenSSL的一个分支</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/libtom/libtomcrypt\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">LibTomCrypt<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：一个非常全面的，模块化的，可移植的加密工具</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/jedisct1/libsodium\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollo