v\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">OpenCV<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：开源计算机视觉库</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/GHamrouni/Recommender\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Recommender<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：使用协同过滤进行产品推荐/建议的C语言库。</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/shogun-toolbox/shogun\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SHOGUN<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：Shogun 机器学习工具</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//code.google.com/p/sofia-ml/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">sofia-ml<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a> ：用于机器学习的快速增量算法套件</li></ul><h3>数学</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//arma.sourceforge.net/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Armadillo<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a> ：高质量的C++线性代数库，速度和易用性做到了很好的平衡。语法和MatlAB很相似</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//code.google.com/p/blaze-lib/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">blaze<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>：高性能的C++数学库，用于密集和稀疏算法。</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//ceres-solver.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">ceres-solver<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a> ：来自谷歌的C++库，用于建模和解决大型复杂非线性最小平方问题。</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.cgal.org/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">CGal<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a>： 高效，可靠的集合算法集合</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//cmldev.net/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">cml<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a> ：用于游戏和图形的免费C++数学库</li><li><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//eigen.tuxfamily.org/\" clas